Title: Animated Jquery Multilevel Menu for Sharepoint 2010
Description:
We have created an easy to use Jquery multilevel animated menu for Sharepoint 2010. 

Useful for front-end sites and intranets and fully customizable.

It supports multilanguaje in Sharepoint Foundation and Entreprise based on a custom list.

It adapts to any default CSS style from Sharepoint and it's fully customizable using the attached custom.css file.
